name: GOGOs Proof-of-Mint
description:
0x10 minted the GOGOs and screen recorded the entire process. It took just under 11 hours from start to finish to randomly generate all 5555.

GOGOs are subjected to many trials and tribulations during their creation; 99.99% of them don’t make it through these tests, and for many who do, the knowledge of how many GOGOs had to perish for them to exist leads to higher than average stress levels.

Once this gruelling process is complete the GOGOs are ranked, carefully placed inside their PODs and loaded up into dispensing machines, ready to be claimed.

Witness the creation of these GOGOs - can you spot yours in the making?
